NAME: Race Track
NOTES: Options: Sim_Endurance.csv , Motor & Track for Sim - Acceleration.csv, Spa_Francorchamps.csv, Autodromo Nazionale Monza.csv, Indianapolis Motor Speedway.csv

NAME: Regen On
NOTES: Determines whether regen is on or not - options: TRUE or FALSE

NAME: Number of Laps
NOTES: Changes depending on number of laps done

NAME: Car Mass
NOTES: Mass of: Chassis, Driver, Accumulator Enclosure, Accumulator Auxillary parts. Missing: Cell Mass, Segment Auxillary Mass, Cooling System Mass

NAME: Max Motor Power
NOTES: ONLY CHANGE BETWEEN THE FOLLOWING THREE VALUES: 10, 20, 40

NAME: Battery Specific Heat Capacity
NOTES: Changes based on battery selection - range from 800-1100

NAME: Heatsink Specific Heat Capacity
NOTES: Changes based on thermal design - range from 400 - 1000

NAME: Air Heat Transfer Coefficient
NOTES: Changes based on thermal design - range from 0-200

NAME: Water Heat Transfer Coefficient
NOTES: Changes based on thermal design - range from 0-400

NAME: Air Cooling Mass Percentage
NOTES: Changes based on thermal design - range from 0-0.05

NAME: Water Cooling Mass Percentage
NOTES: Changes based on thermal design - range from 0.05-0.9
